d"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/frameworks/svelte">Svelte</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Native SSR route importing a same-framework component.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/frameworks/solid">Solid</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Native SSR route importing a same-framework component.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/frameworks/preact">Preact</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Native SSR route importing a same-framework component.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="ds-section"><h2>Streaming</h2><div class="ds-card-grid"><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/streaming/react">React</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Progressive rendering with React Suspense.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/streaming/vue3">Vue 3</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Progressive rendering with Vue Suspense.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/streaming/html">HTML</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Tag-based progressive HTML rendering.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/streaming/solid">Solid</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Progressive rendering with Solid Suspense.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/streaming/preact">Preact</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Progressive rendering with Preact Suspense.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/streaming/html/suspense">HTML suspense</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Native suspense boundaries, nesting, and error recovery.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/streaming/react/shell-error" target="_blank">React shell error (500)</a><p class="ds-card-desc">An error before the shell is emitted returns HTTP 500.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/streaming/vue3/shell-error" target="_blank">Vue 3 shell error (500)</a><p class="ds-card-desc">An error before the shell is emitted returns HTTP 500.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/streaming/html/shell-error" target="_blank">HTML shell error (500)</a><p class="ds-card-desc">An error before the shell is emitted returns HTTP 500.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/streaming/solid/shell-error" target="_blank">Solid shell error (500)</a><p class="ds-card-desc">An error before the shell is emitted returns HTTP 500.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/streaming/preact/shell-error" target="_blank">Preact shell error (500)</a><p class="ds-card-desc">An error before the shell is emitted returns HTTP 500.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="ds-section"><h2>Shadow DOM</h2><div class="ds-card-grid"><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/shadow-dom">Overview</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Explore isolated rendering across every supported route framework.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/shadow-dom/react">React</a><p class="ds-card-desc">React route rendering Widgets in Shadow DOM.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/shadow-dom/html">HTML</a><p class="ds-card-desc">HTML route rendering Widgets in Shadow DOM.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/shadow-dom/vue3">Vue 3</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Vue 3 route rendering Widgets in Shadow DOM.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/shadow-dom/vue2">Vue 2</a><p clas