hing</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Fetch data before rendering widgets.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/request-cache">Request cache</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Deduplicate data within a request.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="ds-section"><h2>Interoperability</h2><div class="ds-card-grid"><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/react-and-vue">Mixed framework page</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Render React and Vue widgets together.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/react-import-widgets">React host</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Import Vue 2 and Vue 3 widgets into React.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/vue3-import-widgets">Vue 3 host</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Import React and Vue 2 widgets into Vue 3.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/vue2-import-widgets">Vue 2 host</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Import React and Vue 3 widgets into Vue 2.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/html-import-widgets">HTML host</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Import framework widgets into an HTML route.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="ds-section"><h2>Integrations</h2><div class="ds-card-grid"><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/dynamic-routes/@web-widget">Dynamic routes</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Filesystem routes with dynamic parameters.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/custom-handlers">Custom handlers</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Control request and response handling.</p></div></div><div class="ds-card"><div class="ds-card-body"><a class="ds-card-link" href="/form">Forms</a><p class="ds-card-desc">Progressively enhanced form submissions.</p></div></di