-card-title">Progress bars</h3><p class="lc-card-text">Animated progress indicators.</p><div class="lc-progress"><div class="lc-progress-bar lc-progress-primary" style="width:75%"></div></div><div class="lc-progress"><div class="lc-progress-bar lc-progress-success" style="width:90%"></div></div></div></div></section><section class="ds-section"><h2>Buttons &amp; alerts</h2><div class="lc-grid"><div class="lc-card"><h3 class="lc-card-title">Buttons</h3><p class="lc-card-text">Various button styles.</p><div class="lc-card-footer"><a href="#" class="lc-btn lc-btn-primary">Primary</a><a href="#" class="lc-btn lc-btn-success">Success</a><a href="#" class="lc-btn lc-btn-danger">Danger</a><a href="#" class="lc-btn lc-btn-outline">Outline</a></div></div><div class="lc-card"><h3 class="lc-card-title">Alerts</h3><div class="lc-alert lc-alert-success">Operation completed successfully.</div><div class="lc-alert lc-alert-danger">An error occurred.</div><div class="lc-alert lc-alert-warning">Please review your input.</div><div class="lc-alert lc-alert-info">Here is some information.</div></div><div class="lc-card"><h3 class="lc-card-title">Stats</h3><div class="lc-stat" style="margin-bottom:12px"><div class="lc-stat-icon">★</div><div><div class="lc-stat-value">12,345</div><div class="lc-stat-label">Total stars</div></div></div><div class="lc-stat"><div class="lc-stat-icon" style="background:var(--sk-green)">✓</div><div><div class="lc-stat-value">98%</div><div class="lc-stat-label">Success rate</div></div></div></div></div></section></main></div><footer><p>This is a footer</p></footer><script>(function(){var m=document.querySelector('[data-playground-menu]');if(!m||m.dataset.enhanced==='true')return;m.dataset.enhanced='true';var p=location.pathname;m.querySelectorAll('a[href]').forEach(function(a){if(a.getAttribute('href')===p)a.setAttribute('aria-current','page')});try{var k='web-router-playground:menu-scroll',s=sessionStorage.getItem(k);if(s!==null)m.scrollTop=Number(s);var save=